wsdl:operation.name: AddDynamicCategory
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Adds a category to the WSUS server.

wsdl:operation.name: AddDynamicCategories
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Adds a collection of dynamic categories to the WSUS server.

wsdl:operation.name: GetDynamicCategory
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets the category that matches the specified name and type.

wsdl:operation.name: GetDynamicCategories
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Gets a set of dynamic categories that satisfy the specified filter criteria.

wsdl:operation.name: SetDynamicCategorySyncStatus
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Sets the update synchronization status of the specified dynamic category to the specified value.
